reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 12, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Talk about transforming my bathroom! Love it!
reviews.reviewText: I recently purchased the VASAGLE Bathroom Floor Storage Cabinet, and I must say, it has been a game changer for my small bathroom. This storage cabinet is perfect for small spaces that need a bright and fresh look.One of the first things that caught my attention about this product is how pleasing it is to the eyes. The clean white color and sleek design instantly added a touch of elegance to my bathroom. It blends seamlessly with my existing decor and enhances the overall look and feel of my small bathroom space for an instant transformation!The storage space provided by this cabinet is impressive. With multiple shelves and drawers, I was able to neatly organize all my bathroom essentials. The drawers glide in and out easily, making accessing items a breeze. I no longer have to rummage through cluttered cabinets to find what I need – everything is right at my fingertips.In addition to its functionality, this storage cabinet is a nice heavy piece. It feels sturdy and well-built, which gives me confidence in its durability. The included anti-tip kit is a thoughtful addition, especially if you have an uneven floor. It provides an extra level of stability, and the best part is that it's not even noticeable.Cleaning this cabinet is a breeze, thanks to its painted coating. A simple wipe with a damp cloth is all it takes to keep it looking spotless. The high-quality materials used in its construction ensure that it will withstand frequent cleaning without losing its luster.When it comes to the price, I was pleasantly surprised. This storage cabinet offers exceptional quality at an affordable price. I shopped around extensively and couldn't find a better deal for a cabinet of this caliber. It's definitely worth the investment.Setting up this cabinet was a breeze, thanks to the easy-to-follow instructions. I was able to assemble it quickly and without any hassle. The package also arrived quicker than I had expected, which was a pleasant surprise.Overall, I couldn't be happier with my purchase. The VASAGLE Bathroom Floor Storage Cabinet is an excellent addition to any small space in need of storage. Its pleasing design, ample storage space, easy gliding drawers, and durable construction make it a must-have. Whether you have a small bathroom or any other area that needs organizing, you can't go wrong with this storage cabinet.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 18, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Looks great, but somewhat small...
reviews.reviewText: This cabinet is small, 11.8 x 23.6 x 31.5 inches. Once assembled, you end up with a little cabinet with 3 relatively small drawers, an adjustable inner shelf (5 options), a door, another shelf and top. Yes, it's small, but so is the price. It may be a little challenging to assemble by yourself (I love the challenge), but it's not too hard. The only reason I slashed a star is because I do not see this able to withstand humidity in a bathroom. It has some decent amount of storage place for any restroom basic needs.

reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Sturdy and easy to assemble
reviews.reviewText: This was the first furniture piece I have ever assembled. Once I unpacked pieces, I started getting nervous. But I decided to just follow manual. I was relieved to see the parts were labeled with a letter and I matched them to the manual. This helped me find the parts so much faster. Everything was so easy after that. Everything fit so easily and it took me 3 hours. But that’s because I REALLY double and triple checked A lot of steps since I was new to assembling. I love my furniture piece. Oh I also love the way the doors close, so smooth.
